Set Name TEMP
Set Size 64 54
Set Background Color black
Set Decorations off
Set Position -0 360
Set Layer Below
Set Sticky on
Set SkipTaskbar on
Set SkipPager on

Rectangle 0 0 64 54 #555555


SetEnv get "wget -o /dev/null -O - http://weather.sh.cvut.cz/export/teplota.php" Overwrite

Text 300 2 0 60 22 #a0a0a0 DejaVuSansCondensed-Bold/7 "SH %.1f °C" Alignment Center
+ exec:${get}:readline:0:scanf:n:"%f"


